{"tid":1539112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"找片段","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T08:54:08.000Z","uid":273967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b54d4684e964f87959cd76f437c654f76f6e3afa","tid":1539112,"uid":273967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FfWfONv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFfWfONv.png&h=dc12f655&s={SIZE}\" />各位有冇呢條片的link ?"},{"pid":"a94dd718ecd617c35467eae1a439b615b8480fdf","tid":1539112,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:55:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人 應承我！<br />\n一日未答應五大訴求 都要繼續上街</span></strong></span><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ea7265b5a329a4bf3929ac640af9dd39aa01dc2","tid":1539112,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:59:55.000Z","msg":"【教學】將Facebook/Youtube 影片文宣轉換成Twitter 文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537277</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 註冊Twitter 帳號。<br />\n2. 找到要post 上Twitter 的影片。<br />\n3. 複制facebook影片連結貼上到以下網頁 (需要登入及縛定Twitter 帳戶， facebook影片分享必需是公開)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://transferring-videos.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransferring-videos.com&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcahTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=98f935d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://transferring-videos.com</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 等待轉換時輸入英文標題，及加上 #chinazi 等 hash tag。<br />\n5. 選擇發佈至 Twitter。<br />\n<br />\n6. 【重要】我諗大家嘅Twitter應該都冇乜人follow, 記得copy自己Twitter post 嘅link, 然後貼上到名人的Twitter post 上！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我做咗幾日已經多咗好多外國人睇，甚至開始有支那打手過黎留言。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4535c8532cdc984b7584211d0328a0c6a4a45d8","tid":1539112,"uid":175424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b54d4684e964f87959cd76f437c654f76f6e3afa","tid":1539112,"uid":273967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FfWfONv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFfWfONv.png&h=dc12f655&s={SIZE}\" />各位有冇呢條片的link ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:36:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/HongKongHermit/status/1165511686406602752\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FHongKongHermit%2Fstatus%2F1165511686406602752&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcahTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=4314b17b\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/HongKongHermit/status/1165511686406602752</a>"},{"pid":"291c5aaae49cd12d2386d03d793bdd99ee65014d","tid":1539112,"uid":273967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4535c8532cdc984b7584211d0328a0c6a4a45d8","tid":1539112,"uid":175424,"like":0